<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/dashboard.css">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="assets/logo.svg" type="image/x-icon">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Sobre | PData</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="sidebar">
        <ul class="logo">
            <li>
                <a href="/dashboard">
                    <img src="assets/logo-xl.svg" alt="">
                </a>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="list-item">
            <li>
                <a href="/dashboard">
                    <span class="material-icons">
                        home
                    </span>
                    Home
                </a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="/club">
                    <span class="material-icons">
                        sports_soccer
                    </span>
                    Clubes
                </a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="/" class="logout">
                    <span class="material-icons">
                        meeting_room
                    </span>
                    Sair
                </a>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="content-header">
            <div class="leagues-box">
                <span class="material-icons">
                    emoji_events
                </span>
                <h2>Campeonatos</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="clubs-box">
                <span class="material-icons">
                    sports_soccer
                </span>
                <h2>Clubes</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="about-box">
                <span class="material-icons">
                    info
                </span>
                <h2>Sobre</h2>
            </div>            
        </div>
        <div class="content-section">
            <div class="box-about box-content" style="background-color: aliceblue; padding: 2rem;">
                <h2>SportsData</h2>
                <p>Criado em 2022, com o intuito de permite o fácil acesso a dados aos fãs do Futebol Brasileiro.</p>
                <p>O SportsData é um projeto, ainda em desenvolvimento, que visa facilitar o acesso a dados dos clubes, campeonatos e seus respectivos jogadores. Atualmente, a aplicação têm o foco apenas no futebol brasileiro.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script>
        let leaguesBox = document.querySelector(".leagues-box");
        leaguesBox.addEventListener("click", () => {
            location.assign("/league")
        })
        let clubsBox = document.querySelector(".clubs-box");
        clubsBox.addEventListener("click", () => {
            location.assign("/club")
        })

        let newsIndex = 1;
        showNews(newsIndex);

        // Next/previous controls
        function nextNews(n) {
            showNews(newsIndex += n);
        }

        // Thumbnail image controls
        function currentNews(n) {
            showNews(newsIndex = n);
        }

        function showNews(n) {
            let i;
            let news = document.getElementsByClassName("item-news");
            let dots = document.getElementsByClassName("dot");

            if (n > news.length) return newsIndex = 1;
            if (n < 1) return newsIndex = news.length;
            for (i = 0; i < news.length; i++) {
                news[i].style.display = "none";
            }
            for (i = 0; i < dots.length; i++) {
                dots[i].className = dots[i].className.replace(" active", "");
            }
            news[newsIndex - 1].style.display = "block";
            dots[newsIndex - 1].className += " active";
        }

    </script>
</body>

</html>